 起鐵路唔太適合</blockquote><br />\n其實淨係返工時間西貢先會無車</blockquote><br />\n其實西貢公路出入九龍係塞到癡線<br />\n所以有鐵路可以解決問題<br />\n但起緊鐵路嘅時候就GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而其他地方就冇咩必要<br />\n如果係話等車耐其實住得西貢就預咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451429378a16591d8aa779816d443d01c7721bcb","tid":305353,"uid":36801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"大東山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: Captv"},{"pid":"e53b061b4730b8ed5f8f3f32490718e14c409a5a","tid":305353,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4e7979db93573b027e3eba1c646bb625d7a87f","tid":305353,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}